    "custom_liquid_yF8yj3": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Custom Liquid",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": false,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "liquid": "<div class=\"phyto-reviews-section\">\n\n  <div class=\"phyto-header\">\n    <h2>Real Women. Real Relief. Real Results.</h2>\n    <div class=\"phyto-rating\">\n      <span class=\"phyto-stars\">★★★★★</span>\n      <strong>4.8/5 Excellent</strong>\n      <span>1,900+ Reviews</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"phyto-carousel\">\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_29_2026_11_41_23_AM.png?v=1782726418 alt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>I stopped dreading meals.</h3>\n      <p>I’m actually getting emotional looking at these side-by-side because I remember exactly how I felt in that first photo. Just stuck and uncomfortable. For so long, I felt like a stranger in my own skin, always hiding behind baggy clothes. But seeing this change... You have no idea how much it means to just feel 'right' and comfortable in your own body for once.</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Heather D.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_28_2026_09_05_34_PM.png?v=1782673573\" alt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>My gut finally feels like mine again.</h3>\n      <p>After my second baby, my digestion was completely wrecked. I looked 6 months pregnant every evening no matter what I ate. This cleared the bloat within days, not weeks. I feel lighter, less puffy, and honestly just better in my body. It's become non-negotiable for me.</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Rebecca C.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/Screenshot_2026-06-19_at_1.05.16_PM.png?v=1781867661\" alt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>More energy every month</h3>\n      <p>My cycle has been more regular since I started. I was diagnosed with PCOS two years ago. My gynecologist recommended I work on inflammation and hormonal balance naturally. After 6 weeks of Phytoseed Labs, my clothes were already looser, 4 cm off my waist. I'm amazed. my cycle became noticeably more regular and my energy improved too !</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Mary B.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/Screenshot_2026-06-28_at_9.09.02_PM.png?v=1782673769\" alt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>I didn't realise how much the bloat was dragging me down.</h3>\n      <p>I was exhausted, uncomfortable, and embarrassed to wear fitted clothes. A friend recommended this and I almost didn't try it. Three weeks later, the puffiness is gone, my energy is back, and I actually want to get dressed in the morning. This is the one thing I tell every woman I know about.</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Stacy M.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/e8d14d2d-b000-4108-847f-643bd8866871.png?v=1782385624\" alt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>The 'Unbuttoning My Pants' era is over</h3>\n      <p>I've had IBS for years and honestly didn't expect much. If you know the struggle of having to unbutton your jeans under the table at dinner because your bloating is so painful, you need this. I'd stopped wearing anything tight because I hated the shape of my belly when I was bloated. I was skeptical about oregano oil, but Phytoseed Labs is the only thing that has actually flattened the bloat and let me wear what I want without fear. It's a total game-changer for my confidence.</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Camilla H.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/86b371ea-76eb-473b-8aa4-a3ed39561d04.jpg?v=1782386464\" alt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>I ate well but still felt bloated</h3>\n      <p>I was eating healthily, but my stomach still felt bloated after nearly every meal. No matter what I tried, nothing seemed to change. Within a few days of taking Phytoseed Labs, I noticed a real difference. Now I can enjoy my meals and dairy without worrying about discomfort afterwards.</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Stephanie M.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_28_2026_09_26_17_PM.png?v=1782674818\" alt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>My gut (and the gas) was ruining my confidence at work.</h3>\n      <p>The stomach noises in meetings. Unbuttoning my jeans under my desk after lunch. Dreading the afternoon because I knew I'd bloat no matter what I ate. I found Phytoseed Labs on a whim and almost didn't bother. Within days I noticed the gurgling had calmed. Within 2 weeks the bloating was gone. I feel sharp, comfortable, and honestly just like myself again.</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Peneloppe T.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"phyto-card\">\n      <img class=\"phyto-review-image\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1076/7378/0573/files/ChatGPT_Image_Jun_28_2026_09_49_19_PM.png?v=1782676192\"\nalt=\"Customer review\">\n      <div class=\"phyto-stars-card\">★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>Not pregnant. Just bloated. Every single day.</h3>\n      <p>I didn't recognise my own body anymore. Bloating used to control my entire life. My doctor had me on so many elimination diets, I felt like I was punishing myself. I was desperate for a natural solution that didn't involve more restrictions. Phytoseed Labs Oregano Oil with Black Seed Oil has been a game-changer. I no longer dread meal times, and the constant heavy feeling is gone. I feel truly comfortable in my own skin. Highly, highly recommend!</p>\n      <div class=\"phyto-author\">Sophie L.</div>\n      <div class=\"phyto-verified\">✓ Verified Purchase</div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.phyto-reviews-section {\n  background: #FAF8F3;\n  padding: 70px 0;\n  overflow: hidden;\n}\n.phyto-header {\n  max-width: 1400px;\n  margin: 0 auto 40px;\n  padding: 0 30px;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 20px;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n}\n.phyto-header h2 {\n  font-size: 42px;\n  line-height: 1.2;\n  color: #2F3527;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n.phyto-rating {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 15px;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n}\n.phyto-stars {\n  color: #00B67A;\n  font-size: 24px;\n  letter-spacing: 3px;\n}\n.phyto-rating strong {\n  font-size: 30px;\n  color: #2F3527;\n}\n.phyto-rating span:last-child {\n  font-size: 24px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  color: #2F3527;\n}\n.phyto-carousel {\n  display: flex;\n  gap: 30px;\n  overflow-x: auto;\n  padding: 0 30px 20px;\n  scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;\n}\n.phyto-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar {\n  height: 6px;\n}\n.phyto-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n  background: #56683F;\n  border-radius: 20px;\n}\n.phyto-card {\n  min-width: 420px;\n  max-width: 420px;\n  background: white;\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  border: 1px solid #EAE7DA;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  scroll-snap-align: start;\n  box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,.05);\n}\n.phyto-review-image {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 260px;\n  object-fit: cover;\n  display: block;\n}\n.phyto-stars-card {\n  color: #00B67A;\n  font-size: 24px;\n  padding: 25px 25px 10px;\n}\n.phyto-card h3 {\n  padding: 0 25px;\n  color: #2F3527;\n  font-size: 32px;\n  line-height: 1.2;\n  margin-bottom: 15px;\n}\n.phyto-card p {\n  padding: 0 25px;\n  color: #4F5F35;\n  font-size: 18px;\n  line-height: 1.8;\n}\n.phyto-author {\n  padding: 20px 25px 5px;\n  font-size: 20px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #2F3527;\n}\n.phyto-verified {\n  padding: 0 25px 25px;\n  color: #00B67A;\n  font-weight: 700;\n}\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .phyto-header h2 { font-size: 28px; }\n  .phyto-rating strong { font-size: 22px; }\n  .phyto-card { min-width: 320px; max-width: 320px; }\n  .phyto-card h3 { font-size: 24px; }\n  .phyto-card p { font-size: 16px; }\n}\n</style>",
